Instead of requiring a special plugin, the major stable update to the WebKit-based web browser includes a new HTML5 getUserMedia API - currently a W3C Editor's Draft - to provide web apps with access to the camera and microphone. For security purposes, users will be prompted to grant apps permission to access the hardware.
